summaries.short: Season One Finale. Alex gets big news and seeks out Tina; Michelle takes a work trip to Sacramentro; Brett spends a day at the beach.
summaries.full: Season One Finale. When Alex gets big career news, he seeks out Tina, who is busy planning her future with Larry. On a trip to Sacramento, Michelle steps up to the plate in a big way. After a day at the beach with the kids, Brett decides to share his feelings with Michelle.

Brett has a chat with David and an honest conversation with Michelle.
